<POST>
<POSTER> Ms. C </POSTER>
<POSTDATE> 2007-11-02T21:57:00 </POSTDATE>
Hello All,
We started this site as a way for communication between teachers and
students.  We are having a problem with members just popping up on our
page without an invite.  How do we delete them so they are off of our
list.  We went into manage members and they are not showing?  Does
anyone know how to fix this problem? If so, it would be greatly
appreciated!! Thank you
</POST>
<POST>
<POSTER> Aldo </POSTER>
<POSTDATE> 2007-11-03T04:43:00 </POSTDATE>
Hello,
It's likely your group settings are on &quot;Anyone can post&quot;. Change them
in &quot;Only members can post&quot;.
On &quot;Anyone can post&quot; everybody around can post even without being a
member and showing up in the member list.
Regards
Aldo

