Reg, if I'm reading this correctly, you're saying that messages are
going to group members email inboxes but are not showing up on the web
site at Google Groups. If this is so, then this means that the spammer
has gleaned group members' email addresses and is sending their crap
to their personal email; which is something that hasn't got anything
to do with groups. The solution for those members would be to block
that address so they don't receive spam from them again. Being a
private group doesn't differentiate to make this scenario possible,
all messages to the group will show on the web site.

Deen

